name: Tierren: Industrial Conglomerate
abilities: If you would place more construction tokens on a spacecraft or megastructure than is required to complete it, then you may place the extra tokens on another spacecraft or megastructure under construction at that asset.

name: Tierren: Megabuilders
abilities: Add 4 construction tokens to Tierren: Megabuilders. You may spend them as generated construction during the resource utilization phase.

name: Tierren: Resilient Infrastructure
abilities: Newly constructed megastructures start with +1 infrastructure

name: Lagrange Construction Yard
abilities: Ships constructed at this asset cost one less construction.

name: Terrarium Project
abilities: You may choose what type of research is generated by this asset.
